&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development Lead&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Business Development team supports the identification and development of new business opportunities. The team has a wide range of functions including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing and supporting new business ideas for growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gathering intelligence on customers and competitors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing customer profiles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing, reviewing and editing bids and proposals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will manage their own workload on a day-to-day basis and act independently to action and prioritise work to meet deadlines. The post holder will work as a key member of the team to ensure that the team’s work programmes are planned and managed effectively and will take a lead in assisting in their successful delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAisha Karefa-SmartJob titleSenior Strategy and Business Development ManagerEmail addressAisha.Karefa-Smart@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
